c (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011210-mero-valdemar">Mero (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011211-corec-valdemar">Corec (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011212-herald-werda">Herald Werda</a>, <a href="/characters/1011213-herald-sylvan">Herald Sylvan</a>, <a href="/characters/1011214-medren-valdemar">Medren (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011215-herald-ylsa">Herald Ylsa</a>, <a href="/characters/1011216-healer-devan">Healer Devan</a>, <a href="/characters/1011217-melidy-valdemar">Melidy (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011218-kyril-valdemar">Kyril (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011219-neave-valdemar">Neave (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011220-christa-valdemar">Christa (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011221-wulf-valdemar">Wulf (Valdemar)</a>, <a href="/characters/1011222-vestel-valdemar">Vestel (Valdemar)</a><span class="toggleLink"><a hide_txt="...less" class="actionLinkLite hideLink" tag="span" href="#" onclick="$j(&#39;#more643&#39;).hide(); $j(&#39;#more_show643&#39;).show();; return false;">...less</a></span></span>
