<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/6783989-kate">Kate</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is the first one in her Heralds of Valdamar series. All of her other books in this universe spin off this book. There are a few (exiles honor/val<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is the first one in her Heralds of Valdamar series. All of her other books in this universe spin off this book. There are a few (exiles honor/valor and such) that are prequels but these were the first written. My suggestion would be read these first by the sword, mage winds, mage storms, exile books, then the rest can be read pretty much in any order. (You don't have to read the owl books series with the res of them and this is the best series out of them all in my opinion) Happy reading!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
